          <p><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">The Solution:</span> We developed a unique strategy focusing on answering questions "like a politician"—a profound method for structuring thoughts and delivering concise, memorable answers.</p>
          <p><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">The Result:</span> Successfully secured a Senior Software Developer role at Google.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Case Study 3 -->
      <article class="h-full rounded-lg bg-white p-8 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 hover:border-primary hover:-translate-y-1 flex flex-col">
